///import Link from 'next/link'
//import Layout from '../components/Layout'

import {Box,Flex, Heading, Input, Text, InputGroup,InputRightElement } from '@chakra-ui/react';
import { EmailIcon, } from '@chakra-ui/icons'

import { Button } from "@chakra-ui/button";

const Login = () => {

    return (
      <Flex height="100vh" alingItems="center" justifyContent="center"  >
        <Flex 
        direction="column" 
        background="#FFFFFF" 
        boxShadow="0px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15)" 
        padding="40px" 
        width="370px"
        height="450px" 
        borderRadius="15px" 
        style={{marginTop:'80px'}}
        >
          <Heading mb={6}  textAlign="center">
            <Text 
            fontFamily="Roboto"
            fontSize="24px"
            fontWeight="900"
            color="#FDC921"
            marginTop="15px"
            >
                GoTokens
            </Text>
            <Text 
            fontFamily="Roboto"
            fontSize="14px"
            fontWeight="700"
            color="#3A3A3A"
            marginTop="12px"
            >
                Entre para começar sua sessão
            </Text>
          </Heading>

          <InputGroup>
            <InputRightElement
                pointerEvents="none"
                color="gray.300"
                fontSize="1.2em"
                children={<EmailIcon color="#3A3A3A" />}
                />
            <Input type="email"  />
           
            </InputGroup>
          
          <Input placeholder=""  mb={6} type="password"/>
          <Button colorScheme="teal"> Log In</Button>
        </Flex>
      </Flex>
    )
}

export default Login;
